Author: BEDBulimic
Text: Removing because   1) Please be articulate in your posts   2) I know you're venting but we don't appreciate spam  3) Unless you're simply venting for the sake of it, as you stated, you need professional help, and I'm sure you've read the rules and sub info that says we don't give any weight loss tips

Author: plantbasedmood
Text: Dude yeah I wasn’t in OA but I was in AA and as hard as I tried to be helped I couldn’t get passed the complete and utter bullshit revolving around “ *my high power* “. Totally, completely unhelpful. Women would just spam call me at 11 pm to check on me but I wouldn’t answer cause I’d be drinking to forget that I had to spend 5 hours a week pretending to buy some thinly veiled Christian bullshit (court ordered, so yeah I had to go)
